{"tid":22314,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［小心中伏］入完數買演唱會飛之後賣家失蹤","createTime":"2016-12-04T11:11:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T14:11:04.000Z","uid":32991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c79efacc6df67d216bf13020e41683483514c5d3","tid":22314,"uid":32991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:11:30.000Z","msg":"好！我承認自己係衰太死蠢，唔介意大家盡情恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n半個月前入左數起Ig一間買演唱會飛（starhk_ticketss)  既Ig shop買左兩張周杰倫演唱會飛，但入數後不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n賣家失蹤，聯絡唔到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qw9B49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qw9B49.jpg&h=f043c981&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講出黎都知一定會比人恥笑，我都覺得自己好蠢。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但唔想有更加多既受害者</strong>"},{"pid":"58e5f2bb9fba1299e87dac7b2ee015b37817428a","tid":22314,"uid":30593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:13:08.000Z","msg":"報左驚未"},{"pid":"c0436a6324198a55f20169facc588a776cd3be79","tid":22314,"uid":32991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>報左驚未</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為唔係香港，諗住聖誕節返香港睇演唱會。<br />\n<br />\n入數係屋企人幫我入，但我先係當時人，所以上網報左警。<br />\n<br />\n希望大家唔好好似我咁蠢，上網買咩都要小心。"},{"pid":"bbe00f7181792b172f70faaf2d6153fd3611c7cb","tid":22314,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:16:10.000Z","msg":"更蠢既係右下。。。。"},{"pid":"8a6ad7707ba8bd9f7c0b65a1388e92ebce970f9e","tid":22314,"uid":13835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T11:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>更蠢既係右下。。。。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n絲打自爆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd3d740e78e41c7baac19b58d900f7c132347623","tid":22314,"uid":2317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"